<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Pending Delivery Reminder - Blue Sky</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f6f9;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333;
        }

        .email-container {
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #ffc107;
            color: #000;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px 20px;
        }

        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 26px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 30px 40px;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .alert-box {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            background-color: #ffc107;
            color: #000;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 15px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #ffc107;
            color: #000;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Blue Sky</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p><strong>Hello <%= user_name %>,</strong></p>

            <p>This is a friendly reminder that the delivery for enquiry <strong>
                    <%= enquiry_id %>
                </strong> is scheduled within the next <strong>2 days</strong>, but we have not yet received
                confirmation of delivery.</p>

            <div class="alert-box">
                <p><strong>Buyer:</strong>
                    <%= buyer_name %>
                </p>
                <p><strong>Expected Delivery Date:</strong>
                    <%= expected_date %>
                </p>
                <p><strong>Status:</strong>
                    <%= status %>
                </p>
            </div>

            <p>Please take the necessary actions to ensure timely delivery or update the system if the goods have
                already been delivered.</p>

            <a href="<%= portal_url %>" class="btn">Check Delivery Status</a>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">We appreciate your prompt attention to this matter.</p>

            <p>Best regards,<br><strong>Blue Sky Logistics Team</strong></p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Blue Sky. All rights reserved.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>